  https://www.codewars.com/kata//525e5a1cb735154b320002c8
  
  You need to return the nth triangular number. You should return 0 for out of range values:

  triangular(0)==0,
  triangular(2)==3,
  triangular(3)==6,
  triangular(-10)==0
  
  function triangular( n ) {
 
return n > 0?  (1/2) * n * (n+1) : 0;
 
 }
